Package Staff.Model

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
Staff.Model.Staff
All Implemented Interfaces:
IEntity
public class Staff extends Object implements IEntity
The Staff class represents a staff member in the system. It implements the IEntity interface and provides details such as ID, name, role, gender, and age.
